ServiceHandler - Class in ie.gmit.sw
ServiceHandler Class, Waits for a doPost() request from a Web Application, The doPost() then calls the doGet() method, Connects to the local Registry and invokes its methods, Adds to an InQueue(Threaded) and deletes from an OutQueue when Tasks are finished, ServiceHandler Refreshes the page every 10Seconds, until the Task given is Completed.
